Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be performed after SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average duration of SW-EIC Reject across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case

Name: Time elapsed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject in variants ending with SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and activity SW-EIC Reject for cases where activity SW-EIC Reject occurs

Name: Average time between SW-Checklist Completed and SW-EIC Reject in rejected submissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time from SW-AE Recommendation overdue to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Recommendation overdue' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time it takes SW-EIC Reject to occur after the first occurrence of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-EIC Reject in direct rejection paths
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-EIC Reject in cases where no reviewer ultimately agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time between the last reminder activity (e.g., Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2) and SW-EIC Reject when reviewers failed to respond
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-EIC Reject in the shortest rejection variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-EIC Reject across all rejection trajectories
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be executed after SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in early-rejection cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
